to !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">These items can be&nbsp;placed into a glass case to protect them safely, prevent them from being twisted into each other and reduce the risk of misplacement.&nbsp;Or you can also put them in a travel underwear bag. It is essential to place these items in a box, be it a paper box, glass case, or a mini backpack to easily remove them and make sure they do not get lost in the backpack or twisted together.</p><p _msttexthash=\"31539768\" _msthash=\"155\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">You can use&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mediadecathlon.com/14/view-15-category.jspz?tokenCheck=NzAxOGZjOTNhMzM3MGVhYzU5ZmVhNDVkMTNkYjNjYTlfOl90b2tlbkNoZWNr&amp;fulltext=8649351)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"\">backpacks that contain multiple compartments</a>&nbsp;for easy division and convenience when you need to place valuables. If you have a computer, place it in the center to protect it from external forces that could damage your computer or phone.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"850\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-cac-loai-balo-chua-nhieu-ngan.jpg\" alt=\"You can use backpacks that contain multiple compartments for easy division and convenience when you need to place valuables \" class=\"wp-image-5873\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-cac-loai-balo-chua-nhieu-ngan.jpg 850w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-cac-loai-balo-chua-nhieu-ngan-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-cac-loai-balo-chua-nhieu-ngan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-cac-loai-balo-chua-nhieu-ngan-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-cac-loai-balo-chua-nhieu-ngan-120x120.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" _mstalt=\"103484329\" _msthash=\"156\" style=\"height: 1508.2px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px; width: 1508.2px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">You can use multi-compartment backpacks for easy division and convenience when you need to put valuables (Source: Internet)</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; overflow-x: auto; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><br></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"Buoc_4_Xep_quan_ao_de_nhan_so_mi_hoac_mot_lop_quan_ao_mong\" _msttexthash=\"2489786\" _msthash=\"170\">Step 4: Fold wrinkled clothes, shirts or a thin layer of clothing</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"68260322\" _msthash=\"171\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Shirts and thin clothes are often one of the types of clothing that easily create wrinkles. If you do not know how to fold correctly, these types of clothes can create additional wrinkles, and if left for a long time, it will become difficult to flatten it. You should place wrinkled shirts or clothes at the top layer. How to fold a shirt while traveling is also very simple:</p><ul style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"5418374\" _msthash=\"172\" style=\"\">Place your shirt and shirt down on a flat surface like the floor, and fold 2 sleeves inward properly.</li><li _msttexthash=\"4128657\" _msthash=\"173\" style=\"\">Next, fold the shirt horizontally so that the edge of the shirt touches the shoulder.</li><li _msttexthash=\"3671928\" _msthash=\"174\" style=\"\">Fold the shirt horizontally again, then fold the sides of the shirt vertically.</li><li _msttexthash=\"3948646\" _msthash=\"175\" style=\"\">Finally, just turn the shirt upside down and put it in your backpack and you\'re done.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"425\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ao-so-mi-va-cac-loai-quan-ao-mong.jpg\" alt=\"Shirts and thin clothes are often one of the types of clothing that easily create wrinkles\" class=\"wp-image-5863\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ao-so-mi-va-cac-loai-quan-ao-mong.jpg 850w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ao-so-mi-va-cac-loai-quan-ao-mong-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ao-so-mi-va-cac-loai-quan-ao-mong-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" _mstalt=\"58569056\" _msthash=\"176\" style=\"height: 762.1px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; width: 1524.2px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Shirts and thin clothes are often one of the types of clothing that easily create wrinkles (Source: Internet)</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; overflow-x: auto; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><br></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"Buoc_5_Tan_dung_khoang_trong_balo_cho_cac_mon_do_con_lai\" _msttexthash=\"2726321\" _msthash=\"187\">Step 5: Take advantage of the backpack space for the remaining items</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"28451319\" _msthash=\"188\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Cosmetics and personal items such as shower gel, shampoo, brushes, and razors should&nbsp;be placed in plastic bags with zippers. This method not only helps to avoid spills, but also makes it easier to see and retrieve the contents of the bag.</p><p _msttexthash=\"12297584\" _msthash=\"189\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Another trick is&nbsp;to put perfume and fragile bottles in socks.&nbsp;Then these socks should be placed between the types of clothing to ensure absolute safety.</p><p _msttexthash=\"37479988\" _msthash=\"190\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">With cloth hats, you can fold them just like clothes, but avoid putting too much stuff on the hat. Depending on your hat style, this may require adjustments to accommodate the concaveness and width of the hat. Avoid tucking too tightly, so that the hat does not stretch wide.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/can-tan-dung-khoang-trong-balo.jpg\" alt=\"Users need to take advantage of the backpack space for the remaining items (\" class=\"wp-image-5865\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/can-tan-dung-khoang-trong-balo.jpg 850w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/can-tan-dung-khoang-trong-balo-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/can-tan-dung-khoang-trong-balo-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" _mstalt=\"26915486\" _msthash=\"191\" style=\"height: 850.39px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px; width: 1512.2px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Users need to take advantage of the backpack space for the remaining items (Source: Internet)</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; overflow-x: auto; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><br></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"Nhung_luu_y_khi_xep_do_du_lich_vao_balo\" _msttexthash=\"1458873\" _msthash=\"204\">Notes when packing travel items into a backpack</span></h2><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Make a list of things to bring</p><p _msttexthash=\"56440969\" _msthash=\"206\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Creating a list of items to bring is an important step to help you identify essential items and avoid carrying unnecessary items. Especially when traveling by plane, with a carry-on luggage&nbsp;limit of 7-12 kilograms, it is extremely important to bring only the things that really matter. When creating your list, consider the following:</p><ul style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"1093378\" _msthash=\"207\" style=\"\">Weather and climate at the tourist site.</li><li _msttexthash=\"2678624\" _msthash=\"208\" style=\"\">The type of travel you choose (relaxation, discovery, business,...).</li><li _msttexthash=\"479258\" _msthash=\"209\" style=\"\">Estimated time for trip.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"456\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tao-danh-sach-cac-vat-dung-can-mang-theo.jpg\" alt=\"Creating a list of items to bring is an important step to help you determine what items you need \" class=\"wp-image-5874\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tao-danh-sach-cac-vat-dung-can-mang-theo.jpg 850w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tao-danh-sach-cac-vat-dung-can-mang-theo-300x161.jpg 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tao-danh-sach-cac-vat-dung-can-mang-theo-768x412.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" _mstalt=\"81088215\" _msthash=\"210\" style=\"height: 805.35px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px; width: 1501.2px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Creating a list of items to bring is an important step to help you determine what you need (Source: Internet)</figcaption></figure><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Tags, labels to mark utensils</p><p _msttexthash=\"54903121\" _msthash=\"213\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Using tags and tags is a smart way&nbsp;to mark and recognize items while traveling. Choose highlight color tags to classify, assign featured images or icons for quick identification. At the same time, record contact information and use anti-loss tags to protect important items. These measures help manage your baggage efficiently.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"527\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-tag-va-mac-la-cach-thong-minh.jpg\" alt=\"Using tags and tags is a smart way to mark and recognize items while traveling\" class=\"wp-image-5875\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-tag-va-mac-la-cach-thong-minh.jpg 850w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-tag-va-mac-la-cach-thong-minh-300x186.jpg 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/su-dung-tag-va-mac-la-cach-thong-minh-768x476.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" _mstalt=\"37153558\" _msthash=\"214\" style=\"height: 931.984px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; width: 1503.2px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Using tags and labels is a smart way to mark and recognize items when traveling (Source: Internet)</figcaption></figure><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Compartment between smelly items</p><p _msttexthash=\"49379889\" _msthash=\"217\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">To prevent scents from items in your luggage,&nbsp;use anti-odor or plastic bags to protect each group of items separately.&nbsp;Wrapping things in plastic bags can help keep the scent from spreading to other items. Place strongly scented items in a tightly sealed container for isolation and use a vacuum bag to remove air.</p><p _msttexthash=\"62080577\" _msthash=\"218\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Add a light fragrance or desiccant bag to your luggage&nbsp;to control odors and keep the air inside the bag dry. This way, you can keep your luggage clean at all times. Furthermore, you should put your money, wallet, ID, and bank card in a separate compartment or safety bag in your briefcase to prevent theft and to make it easy to retrieve when you need to use it.</p>', '2024-03-06', 0);
