(68, 'What does it take to go hiking? 15+ climbing essentials', '1709919631_68.png', '<br><p style=\"margin-block: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">What are the essential items for the climb? Or what to prepare for climbing is always a question of those who love this subject, especially those who do not have too much experience. Don\'t climb right away, but let\'s take a look at the list of 15+ minimum climbing items for the most convenient trip.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; overflow-x: auto; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"></figure><p _msttexthash=\"2758509\" _msthash=\"77\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"1_Giay_leo_nui_chuyen_dung\" _msttexthash=\"603564\" _msthash=\"94\">1. Specialized hiking boots</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"32113952\" _msthash=\"95\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">One of the most essential climbing items is specialized hiking boots. Preparing hiking boots will help protect the feet from external impacts. Thereby limiting scratches and sprains when having to move for a long time in rugged steep rocky terrain.</p><p _msttexthash=\"11993163\" _msthash=\"96\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">In addition, this climbing gear also helps to keep feet warm in cold weather conditions, while providing stability for climbers, avoiding slippery.</p><p _msttexthash=\"6837935\" _msthash=\"97\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Depending on the difficulty of the route, you can use bata shoes. But trekking shoes are still the better choice.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2526472\" _msthash=\"98\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">How to choose the right hiking boots in Vietnam:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"28789878\" _msthash=\"100\">Suitable for the terrain: Choose trekking shoes based on the terrain, for example with river and stream terrain, so prioritize good waterproof shoes. The rocky terrain is more suitable for hiraffes that have a groove design at the sole.</li><li _msttexthash=\"12176086\" _msthash=\"101\">High durability: It is necessary to choose hiking boots with good friction, limited slippage and high durability, resistant to external influences.</li><li _msttexthash=\"17761536\" _msthash=\"102\">Bring comfort to users: An ideal hiking shoe should have an inner lining that possesses moderate smoothness and elasticity, providing comfort while remaining flexible when moving.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-chon-giay-leo-nui-co-do-ma-sat-tot-han-che-tron-truot.png\" alt=\"It is recommended to choose hiking boots with good friction, limiting slippage\" class=\"wp-image-2404\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-chon-giay-leo-nui-co-do-ma-sat-tot-han-che-tron-truot.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-chon-giay-leo-nui-co-do-ma-sat-tot-han-che-tron-truot-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-chon-giay-leo-nui-co-do-ma-sat-tot-han-che-tron-truot-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"26153764\" _msthash=\"103\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">It is recommended to choose hiking boots with good friction, limiting slippage</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"2_Trang_phuc_leo_nui_chuyen_dung\" _msttexthash=\"730314\" _msthash=\"105\">2. Specialized climbing attire</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"26537017\" _msthash=\"106\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">One of the items that cannot be forgotten when climbing is specialized hiking clothing. These clothes are often designed with special designs and materials, providing comfort and flexibility for the wearer during movement.</p><p _msttexthash=\"61219782\" _msthash=\"107\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Many people think that it is possible to take advantage of normal clothes if it is cool. However, there are still summer hiking clothing or specialized trekking gear for all weather. In general, specialized climbing clothing will protect you from harsh weather conditions in the high mountains as well as influences from the outside environment.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2525588\" _msthash=\"108\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p _msttexthash=\"5587205\" _msthash=\"109\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing hiking attire: Whether it\'s women\'s or men\'s, you need to consider the following:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"24576630\" _msthash=\"110\">Suitable for weather and terrain: If the weather is hot or cool, you should give preference to clothes with absorbent materials. If in cold weather, rain, you should prepare an umbrella jacket, waterproof windbreaker.</li><li _msttexthash=\"16084367\" _msthash=\"111\">Choosing the right material: Choose clothes made from durable materials that have high elasticity while absorbing sweat well. Some of those suggestions are cotton, khaki,...</li><li _msttexthash=\"8317673\" _msthash=\"112\">Pay attention to compactness: Prioritize lightweight clothing that can be easily stored on the move, such as wind jackets.</li><li _msttexthash=\"30674865\" _msthash=\"113\">Some clothes should be limited when climbing: For hiking pants, it is recommended to limit those that are too short or tight to the legs that make it difficult to exercise. It is best to choose specialized hiking pants or trousers of medium width.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe.png\" alt=\"Priority should be given to lightweight clothes that create flexibility when moving\" class=\"wp-image-2406\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"32227208\" _msthash=\"114\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Priority should be given to lightweight clothes that create flexibility when moving</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"3_Do_an_giau_nang_luong_va_nuoc_uong_bu_dien_giai\" _msttexthash=\"1750684\" _msthash=\"116\">3. Energy foods and electrolyte rehydration drinks</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"33204093\" _msthash=\"117\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">In a long climbing journey with many difficulties, it is extremely necessary to prepare drinking water and takeaway food to the mountain. These items will help you always maintain good physical fitness while avoiding hypoglycemia or loss of strength.</p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when preparing food and drinks:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"9647820\" _msthash=\"119\">Number of food to bring: You can balance the amount of food and water you bring based on the number of people and the duration of the trip.</li><li _msttexthash=\"7945561\" _msthash=\"120\">Some foods to prepare: For the day hike, prioritize junk food such as dry food, cereal, instant noodles, bread, sausages,...</li><li _msttexthash=\"3282370\" _msthash=\"121\">Besides, you should also prepare filtered water instead of energy drinks.</li><li _msttexthash=\"10560043\" _msthash=\"122\">In addition to the familiar hiking food, you can consider bringing energy bars, glucose packets in case the body loses strength and fatigue.</li></ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"4_Thuoc_dau_bung_thuoc_tieu_chay_va_cac_thiet_bi_y_te_co_ban\" _msttexthash=\"2500199\" _msthash=\"123\">4. Abdominal pain, diarrhea medicines and basic medical devices</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"22702160\" _msthash=\"124\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Never climb a mountain without you having the necessary medical supplies prepared. This preparation will ensure the safety of climbers in case of emergencies such as illness, sun cold, allergies,... or trauma.</p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Notes when preparing medical equipment:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"5428098\" _msthash=\"126\">Medicines to prepare: Colic, antipyretic, anti-inflammatory, diarrheal, effervescent tablets</li><li _msttexthash=\"18769738\" _msthash=\"127\">What medical equipment to prepare: You should bring a full range of equipment such as first aid kits such as dressings, cold medicines, painkillers, antibiotics, vitamins, insect sprays ,...</li><li _msttexthash=\"7252089\" _msthash=\"128\">How to store: Place all of this medical equipment in a small bag and make sure it\'s easy to remove in case of emergency.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chuan-bi-nhung-thiet-bi-y-te-co-ban.png\" alt=\"Prepare basic medical equipment to ensure stable health\" class=\"wp-image-2401\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chuan-bi-nhung-thiet-bi-y-te-co-ban.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chuan-bi-nhung-thiet-bi-y-te-co-ban-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chuan-bi-nhung-thiet-bi-y-te-co-ban-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"47761454\" _msthash=\"129\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Prepare basic medical equipment to ensure stable health</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"5_Balo_leo_nui_chua_nhieu_ngan\" _msttexthash=\"1470703\" _msthash=\"131\">5. Hiking backpack contains many compartments</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"22082710\" _msthash=\"132\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">A dedicated hiking backpack cannot be included in the list of essential items for travel. They are usually designed with many compartments and small bags that make it easy to store all items during the trip.</p><p _msttexthash=\"16308461\" _msthash=\"133\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Especially with the strap, the backpack will reduce the pressure on the body, helping climbers maintain strength and flexibility when moving on rugged mountainous terrain.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2525926\" _msthash=\"134\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p _msttexthash=\"954265\" _msthash=\"135\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing a hiking backpack:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"16033875\" _msthash=\"136\">Choose the right backpack capacity: You should balance the number of items you carry and your physical condition and body weight to use a backpack with appropriate capacity.</li><li _msttexthash=\"10957609\" _msthash=\"137\">Use a high-strength hiking backpack: Prioritize backpacks with a large capacity, easy to pick up and made from durable, waterproof materials.</li><li _msttexthash=\"6977633\" _msthash=\"138\">Lightweight backpack selection: The ideal climbing backpack should be lightweight, which can be easily folded.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nguoi-leo-nui-nen-chuan-bi-dien-thoai-sac-du-phong-dao.png\" alt=\"Climbers should prepare some items such as phones, power banks, knives ,...\" class=\"wp-image-2407\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nguoi-leo-nui-nen-chuan-bi-dien-thoai-sac-du-phong-dao.png 800w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nguoi-leo-nui-nen-chuan-bi-dien-thoai-sac-du-phong-dao-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nguoi-leo-nui-nen-chuan-bi-dien-thoai-sac-du-phong-dao-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" _mstalt=\"43889222\" _msthash=\"139\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Climbers should prepare some items such as phones, power banks, knives ,...</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"6_Ao_mua_leo_nui\" _msttexthash=\"368537\" _msthash=\"141\">6. Climbing raincoat</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"41159339\" _msthash=\"142\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Although before starting the journey, you always preview the weather forecast and choose to go into the climbing season, encountering unusual conditions is inevitable. During the climbing journey, sometimes you will encounter not very ideal weather conditions such as rain, fog.</p><p _msttexthash=\"35412520\" _msthash=\"143\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Therefore, preparing raincoats for the trip is extremely necessary. This item helps the body stay dry and warm, limiting the influence of rain and wind or cold temperatures. From there, it helps climbers always maintain a stable body temperature and good health.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2483624\" _msthash=\"144\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing a raincoat:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"10024833\" _msthash=\"146\">Use a durable raincoat: Climbers should prioritize choosing raincoats with good durability and light weight, easy to fit in a backpack.</li><li _msttexthash=\"9054669\" _msthash=\"147\">Care about water resistance: Choosing a raincoat with effective waterproof will ensure the most favorable operation process.</li><li _msttexthash=\"5353894\" _msthash=\"148\">Some suitable suggestions for the hike are a lightweight raincoat and a bat-wing Poncho raincoat.</li></ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"7_Dien_thoai_va_sac_du_phong_PowerBox\" _msttexthash=\"765271\" _msthash=\"149\">7. Phone and power bank (PowerBox)</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"44897736\" _msthash=\"150\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">When climbing, there is definitely no wifi and almost no 4G but there can still be phone coverage. So, before climbing, you need to save the number of the climbing poster, or the commune phone number of the ward you are climbing. If there is any problem, you can still contact the outside to call for help.</p><p _msttexthash=\"8269118\" _msthash=\"151\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Power banks (PowerBox) always ensure adequate power supply for smartphones and other technology items during the climb.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2483793\" _msthash=\"152\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing a phone and power bank:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"3990753\" _msthash=\"154\">It is recommended to choose power banks above 10,000mAh and light weight less than 500 g.</li><li _msttexthash=\"3526471\" _msthash=\"155\">There is no need to bring wifi because there is almost no 4G signal in the forest.</li><li _msttexthash=\"14639014\" _msthash=\"156\">Essential applications for the climb can be mentioned as <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.maps&hl=vi\" _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"\">Google Maps</a>, <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.polestar.accuweather.production.android&hl=vi\" _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"\">Accuweather</a> weather application, GPS <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.eclipsim.gpsstatus2&hl=vi\" _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"\">Status & Toolbox</a> high-precision compass application, etc</li></ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"8_Kem_chong_muoi\" _msttexthash=\"606645\" _msthash=\"157\">8. Mosquito repellent cream</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"22859408\" _msthash=\"158\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Alpine is the ideal growing conditions for many types of mosquitoes, insects. So if you plan to hike overnight, you should bring mosquito repellent creams to protect yourself from the attack of these animals.</p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing mosquito repellent cream:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"41316704\" _msthash=\"160\">Consider the composition carefully before choosing a mosquito repellent cream: You should only carry this product when you are not sensitive to any ingredients. It is best to test the drug on a small area of skin, ensuring that no irritation, rashes appear to be used for the whole body.</li><li _msttexthash=\"22109035\" _msthash=\"161\">Instructions on how to apply properly: Mosquito repellent can be applied to hands, feet or blankets to prevent insects. When using, it is necessary to avoid some places such as eyes, nose, mouth, open wounds.</li></ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"9_Tui_nguleu\" _msttexthash=\"356486\" _msthash=\"162\">9. Sleeping bag/tent</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"30299984\" _msthash=\"163\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">For overnight trips, preparing extra items for climbing such as tents or sleeping bags is a necessary application for the climb. This item provides a good night\'s sleep while protecting you from adverse weather conditions or insect attacks.</p><p _msttexthash=\"3373812\" _msthash=\"164\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing tents and sleeping bags against mosquitoes:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"6781944\" _msthash=\"166\">Choosing the right tent size: Climbers can base on the number of climbing members to choose the right tent size.</li><li _msttexthash=\"72346144\" _msthash=\"167\">Care about the quality of camping tents and sleeping bags: It is recommended to use a camping tent of moderate weight suitable for long distances while being durable and waterproof. With sleeping bags, it is necessary to pay attention to comfort, heat retention as well as compactness. It is best to first choose to buy tents and sleeping bags from reputable brands like Decathlon.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/lua-chon-nhung-loai-leu-tui-ngu-uy-tin.png\" alt=\"Choose tents and sleeping bags from reputable brands\" class=\"wp-image-2403\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/lua-chon-nhung-loai-leu-tui-ngu-uy-tin.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/lua-chon-nhung-loai-leu-tui-ngu-uy-tin-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/lua-chon-nhung-loai-leu-tui-ngu-uy-tin-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"30713891\" _msthash=\"168\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Choose tents and sleeping bags from reputable brands</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"10_Dung_cu_sinh_ton\" _msttexthash=\"312039\" _msthash=\"170\">10. Survival tools</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"19368037\" _msthash=\"171\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Essential items for climbing related to survival such as whistles, compasses, lighters, maps ,... will assist us in emergencies such as getting lost or having to spend a night in the mountains.</p><p _msttexthash=\"23049520\" _msthash=\"172\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">With the necessary items when climbing the mountain, it will be easier for climbers to determine the direction or give a signal for help to everyone. From there, ensure safety in case unexpected incidents occur.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2356926\" _msthash=\"173\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing survival tools:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"10878998\" _msthash=\"175\">Consider the number of instruments: You should only bring really necessary tools, prioritize light items, can be stored in a backpack easily.</li><li _msttexthash=\"17371640\" _msthash=\"176\">Make sure all tools are working properly: Before you bring it, you should check all of the above tools to determine that they work properly, thereby avoiding mishaps during the trip.</li></ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"11_Gay_leo_nui\" _msttexthash=\"332722\" _msthash=\"177\">11. Climbing sticks</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"23292022\" _msthash=\"178\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Hiking sticks are considered a close friend for backpackers on the journey to conquer new roads. This item works to reduce the weight load exerted on the legs while allocating them to the shoulders, hands and back.</p><p _msttexthash=\"29914755\" _msthash=\"179\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">As a result, it helps reduce leg fatigue, limit injuries and protect knee health when moving for a long time. In addition, climbing also supports you to maintain better balance, improve endurance and endurance when facing difficult terrain.</p><p _msttexthash=\"10993125\" _msthash=\"180\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Hiking sticks are often thought of as professional climbing tools, but in fact, this is an indispensable item for you in all mountain terrains.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2524873\" _msthash=\"181\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing a hiking stick:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"5797389\" _msthash=\"183\">Pay attention to compactness: Prefer to choose climbing sticks that can be stowed and carried easily.</li><li _msttexthash=\"11583091\" _msthash=\"184\">Material selection of sticks: Choose sticks made from aluminum alloys so that this item enhances rigidity while effectively minimizing weight.</li><li _msttexthash=\"12109253\" _msthash=\"185\">Choice of multi-purpose hiking sticks: You can also use climbing sticks that integrate some additional functions such as compass, whistle, camera ,...</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/gay-leo-nui-ho-tro-giu-thang-bang.png\" alt=\"Hiking sticks support balance, enhance endurance and limit injuries\" class=\"wp-image-2402\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/gay-leo-nui-ho-tro-giu-thang-bang.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/gay-leo-nui-ho-tro-giu-thang-bang-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/gay-leo-nui-ho-tro-giu-thang-bang-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"43912128\" _msthash=\"186\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Hiking sticks support balance, enhance endurance and limit injuries</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"12_Gang_tay_leo_nui\" _msttexthash=\"333073\" _msthash=\"188\">12. Climbing gloves</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"38416092\" _msthash=\"189\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Gloves help resist water, keep warm while protecting your hands from the effects of the outside environment. In addition, the support of this item will contribute to increasing friction in difficult passages that require the support of ropes, making this process easier.</p><p _msttexthash=\"2483897\" _msthash=\"190\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"11955138\" _msthash=\"192\">Selection of gloves of good quality: It is recommended to choose long-fingered gloves that provide good resistance, protect the safety of the hands.</li><li _msttexthash=\"12045709\" _msthash=\"193\">Interested in the material: The material for making gloves should be durable, waterproof and effectively absorb moisture and evapotranspiration.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-lua-chon-gang-tay-chong-tham-nuoc.png\" alt=\"It is recommended to choose good waterproof gloves while effectively absorbing moisture and evapotranspiration\" class=\"wp-image-2405\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-lua-chon-gang-tay-chong-tham-nuoc.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-lua-chon-gang-tay-chong-tham-nuoc-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nen-lua-chon-gang-tay-chong-tham-nuoc-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"47384896\" _msthash=\"194\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">It is recommended to choose good waterproof gloves while effectively absorbing moisture and evapotranspiration</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"13_Kinh_mat_mu_bo_goi\" _msttexthash=\"846352\" _msthash=\"196\">13. Eyeglasses, hats, pillowcases</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"6073314\" _msthash=\"197\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">In addition to basic climbing attire, you can also consider bringing some climbing accessories such as:</p><ul style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"1803529\" _msthash=\"198\">Eyeglasses: Protect your eyes from smog or sunlight.</li><li _msttexthash=\"10210902\" _msthash=\"199\">Hat: Prevent heat stroke, help the body always maintain the ideal temperature while keeping a good state and spirit throughout the trip.</li><li _msttexthash=\"2457091\" _msthash=\"200\">Pillow bundle: Protect the body from injuries during climbing.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Note when choosing climbing accessories:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"15352987\" _msthash=\"202\">Pay attention to the characteristics of the climbing area: You should consider what to bring based on the needs and weather characteristics, terrain of the climbing area.</li><li _msttexthash=\"11307400\" _msthash=\"203\">Prioritize light clothing: Choosing clothes that are light in weight and folded easily will make the movement process easier and more flexible.</li></ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"14_Vat_dung_bo_sung\" _msttexthash=\"366028\" _msthash=\"204\">14. Additional items</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"4312295\" _msthash=\"205\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">To ensure the most convenient climb, you should also prepare additional items such as:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"2578914\" _msthash=\"206\">Knife: Can be used to peel fruit, cut food or defend in emergencies.</li><li _msttexthash=\"2804737\" _msthash=\"207\">Sunscreen: Protects the skin from the effects of UV rays in sunlight.</li><li _msttexthash=\"10014433\" _msthash=\"208\">GPS navigation device: Make it easy to find directions when your phone or map isn\'t available, and assist in your search for emergencies.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><br></figure><p _msttexthash=\"4804475\" _msthash=\"211\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">In addition to fully preparing the above items, you also need to note some things as follows:</p><ul class=\"has-background\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; padding: 1.25em 2.375em; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(226,=\"\" 238,=\"\" 250);=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"30861064\" _msthash=\"212\">Optimizing the number of things to carry: You should not carry too many things, but only bring the most necessary items to create convenience and flexibility when moving. It\'s best to make a list of items to prepare to make sure no items are missed.</li><li _msttexthash=\"39465699\" _msthash=\"213\">Prepare yourself in advance for good physical fitness: The climbing journey requires participants to have enough endurance, perseverance as well as alertness. So prepare yourself for good physical fitness through bodybuilding exercises to have the most convenient trip.</li><li _msttexthash=\"9582664\" _msthash=\"214\">Learn how to use survival items: Understanding how to use all the items you prepare will help you be more proactive in bad situations.</li><li _msttexthash=\"36438545\" _msthash=\"215\">Learn about the climbing site in advance: You can refer to some information on the internet or through the actual sharing of the previous person about the area where you will participate in the climb. From there, draw experiences for yourself in the upcoming journey.</li><li _msttexthash=\"30676100\" _msthash=\"216\">Interested in the weather forecast: Before departing, you should follow the weather forecast to ensure your journey is the most convenient as well as prepare your gear to deal with harsh weather conditions such as rain, sunshine, strong wind.</li><li _msttexthash=\"12067419\" _msthash=\"217\">Choose to climb with a guide or native: If you do not have too much climbing experience, ask for the help of a guide or native for the most convenient trip</li></ul><br>', '2024-03-06', 0);
