(69, 'Suggest the 20+ most trendy safe, comfortable climbing outfits in 2024', '1709919654_69.png', '<p style=\"margin-block: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Choosing the right climbing outfit not only helps you move flexibly and safely but also helps you have impressive \"virtual life\" photos. In the article below, let\'s take a look at the 20+ most popular climbing outfits with Decathlon today!<br><br><br><br><br></p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" _msttexthash=\"2231359\" _msthash=\"35\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; line-height: 1.25; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">1. Advice on choosing a safe and fashionable climbing outfit</h1><p _msttexthash=\"2659007\" _msthash=\"36\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Here are 5 basic rules to help you choose the right climbing outfit:<br>1.1 Choose an outfit based on location and climbing time</p><p _msttexthash=\"44219591\" _msthash=\"56\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">You should choose the right climbing outfit for the location and time you plan. It is best to preview the weather forecast to prepare the right outfit. At the same time, refer to the experiences of previous participants to avoid choosing the wrong outfit to affect the experience during the trip.</p><p style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Example:</p><ul style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"18530876\" _msthash=\"58\">For a summer climb, you should choose models of pants and hiking jackets that are thin and light, have high elasticity and absorb sweat well. Also bring accessories such as hats, eyeglasses.</li><li _msttexthash=\"32257368\" _msthash=\"59\">For a winter climb, you can combine a thermal jacket, a long-sleeved sweater, and a sweatshirt or float jacket to keep your body warm. In addition, if the climbing area often gets a lot of rain, preparing raincoats and waterproof shoes is also essential.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/xem-dia-diem-va-thoi-gian-de-chon-outfit-leo-nui-phu-hop.png\" alt=\"Pay attention to the location and time of climbing to choose the right outfit\" class=\"wp-image-3108\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/xem-dia-diem-va-thoi-gian-de-chon-outfit-leo-nui-phu-hop.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/xem-dia-diem-va-thoi-gian-de-chon-outfit-leo-nui-phu-hop-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/xem-dia-diem-va-thoi-gian-de-chon-outfit-leo-nui-phu-hop-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"25364742\" _msthash=\"60\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Pay attention to the location and time of climbing to choose the right outfit</figcaption></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; line-height: 1.4; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"12_Lua_chon_trang_phuc_nhieu_lop\" _msttexthash=\"643981\" _msthash=\"62\">1.2 Choice of layered outfits</span></h3><p _msttexthash=\"13497185\" _msthash=\"63\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">This will help climbers to be more active in the different weather conditions of the trip. Basically, you should prepare a full range of costumes when climbing:</p><ul style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"7903480\" _msthash=\"64\">Moisture resistant layer: usually thin underwear that dries quickly and is especially soft, comfortable for the skin.</li><li _msttexthash=\"7189741\" _msthash=\"65\">Thermal layer: can be a thin and light long-sleeved or short-sleeved T-shirt, providing flexibility when moving.</li><li _msttexthash=\"11771604\" _msthash=\"66\">Insulation: this is necessary clothing for low temperature areas, depending on the weather situation, you can prepare a life jacket or wind jacket.</li><li _msttexthash=\"6290128\" _msthash=\"67\">Wind resistance: the ideal option would be a raincoat or a light shirt with a hat with good waterproofness.</li></ul><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trang-phuc-co-nhieu-lop-giup-ban-chu-dong.png\" alt=\"Layered outfits help you be active in all weather conditions \" class=\"wp-image-3107\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trang-phuc-co-nhieu-lop-giup-ban-chu-dong.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trang-phuc-co-nhieu-lop-giup-ban-chu-dong-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trang-phuc-co-nhieu-lop-giup-ban-chu-dong-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"46736248\" _msthash=\"68\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Layered outfits help you be active in all weather conditions</figcaption></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; line-height: 1.4; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"13_Su_dung_trang_phuc_co_chat_lieu_phu_hop\" _msttexthash=\"1336491\" _msthash=\"70\">1.3 Use clothing with appropriate materials</span></h3><p _msttexthash=\"9513439\" _msthash=\"71\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">The right clothing material will help your trip be safe, avoid skin scratches and still ensure comfort and flexibility in movement.</p><p _msttexthash=\"1100970\" _msthash=\"72\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Some fabrics you should prioritize are:</p><ul style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><li _msttexthash=\"2703103\" _msthash=\"73\">Stretchy cotton fabric absorbs sweat well, dries quickly and cool.</li><li _msttexthash=\"3847116\" _msthash=\"74\">The khaki fabric is wrinkle-free and durable, suitable for hiking jackets/pants.</li><li _msttexthash=\"2912572\" _msthash=\"75\">Woolen fabric gives good warmth for climbing trips in the cold season.</li><li _msttexthash=\"1456767\" _msthash=\"76\">Felt fabric helps to keep warm well, breathable.</li></ul><p _msttexthash=\"23308129\" _msthash=\"77\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">In addition, when choosing underwear you should give preference to synthetic materials such as polyester or merino wool to absorb sweat well. Conversely, you should avoid choosing underwear made from cotton.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chat-lieu-co-do-ben-cao-thoang-khi-tham-hut-mo-hoi-tot.png\" alt=\"Clothing materials need to be durable, breathable, and absorb sweat well \" class=\"wp-image-3089\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chat-lieu-co-do-ben-cao-thoang-khi-tham-hut-mo-hoi-tot.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chat-lieu-co-do-ben-cao-thoang-khi-tham-hut-mo-hoi-tot-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chat-lieu-co-do-ben-cao-thoang-khi-tham-hut-mo-hoi-tot-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"42807817\" _msthash=\"78\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px; width: 840px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Clothing materials need to be durable, breathable, and absorb sweat well</figcaption></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; line-height: 1.4; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"14_Uu_tien_nhung_outfit_gon_nhe\" _msttexthash=\"949949\" _msthash=\"80\">1.4 Prioritize lightweight outfits</span></h3><p _msttexthash=\"23699247\" _msthash=\"81\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">The climbing journey usually takes place for a long time with many difficulties due to terrain and weather factors. Therefore, using too bulky clothes will make climbers lose strength and have difficulty moving.</p><p _msttexthash=\"19390397\" _msthash=\"82\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Instead, prioritize lightweight outfits that can be stowed away easily. Some suggestions for you with hiking clothes according to this criterion are T-shirts, muscle tights, wind jackets,...</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"567\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe.jpg\" alt=\"Preference should be given to lightweight clothes that do not cause difficulties when moving \" class=\"wp-image-3109\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe.jpg 850w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/uu-tien-nhung-trang-phuc-gon-nhe-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" _mstalt=\"20550530\" _msthash=\"83\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Preference should be given to lightweight clothes that do not cause difficulties when moving</figcaption></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; line-height: 1.4; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"15_Chon_trang_phuc_co_do_ben_cao_va_chong_tham_nuoc_tot\" _msttexthash=\"1654744\" _msthash=\"85\">1.5 Choose clothes that are durable and waterproof</span></h3><p _msttexthash=\"25671672\" _msthash=\"86\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">When choosing, you also need to pay attention to the material and technology of sewing costumes. To Decathlon suggest some materials with high strength and effective waterproofing such as polyester, nylon, PVC, Gore-Tex,...</p><p _msttexthash=\"14499706\" _msthash=\"87\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">High-strength and waterproof hiking clothing protects the wearer from a variety of terrain conditions such as rocky mountains, steep hills or rivers and streams.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; clear: both; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); display: table;\" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/su-dung-outfit-leo-nui-co-do-ben-cao.png\" alt=\"Using a high-strength climbing outfit provides the best protection for the wearer \" class=\"wp-image-3104\" srcset=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/su-dung-outfit-leo-nui-co-do-ben-cao.png 1000w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/su-dung-outfit-leo-nui-co-do-ben-cao-300x200.png 300w, https://www.decathlon.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/su-dung-outfit-leo-nui-co-do-ben-cao-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" _mstalt=\"52232895\" _msthash=\"88\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 10px;\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; caption-side: bottom; display: table-caption;\">Using a high-strength climbing outfit provides the best protection for the wearer</figcaption></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"2_Cach_lua_chon_outfit_leo_nui_phu_hop\" _msttexthash=\"1164059\" _msthash=\"90\">2. How to choose the right climbing outfit</span></h2><p _msttexthash=\"5763875\" _msthash=\"91\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">A climbing outfit that ensures both safety and fashion elements should meet the following criteria:</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; line-height: 1.4; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"21_Giay_leo_nui\" _msttexthash=\"243425\" _msthash=\"92\">2.1 Hiking boots</span></h3><p _msttexthash=\"9324588\" _msthash=\"93\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><a href=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/vi/hiking-trekking/giay-leo-nui-12847\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"\">Hiking boots</a> are an essential item that protects your feet from injury while helping you move easily on complex mountain terrain.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;=\"\" margin-right:=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">            Should<ul><li _msttexthash=\"4820777\" _msthash=\"96\">Choose specialized hiking boots that are durable, good friction and effective waterproof.</li><li _msttexthash=\"10153572\" _msthash=\"97\">Choose shoes with a smooth and elastic inner lining, good for both hugging the feet and not causing restraint and discomfort when moving.</li><li _msttexthash=\"2822391\" _msthash=\"98\">Choose a hiking shoe size that is 0.5 to 1 size larger than normal shoes.<br>Don\'t<br></li></ul><ul><li _msttexthash=\"1591304\" _msthash=\"99\">Choose hiking boots that are too tight or too wide.</li><li _msttexthash=\"5379270\" _msthash=\"100\">Choosing shoes that are too stiff makes it difficult to move and easily causes the feet to blister.</li><li _msttexthash=\"5527717\" _msthash=\"101\">Limit the use of fashion shoes or ordinary running shoes when climbing mountains in harsh terrain.</li></ul></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; line-height: 1.4; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><span id=\"22_Ao_leo_nui\" _msttexthash=\"594191\" _msthash=\"102\">2.2 Mountaineering jackets</span></h3><p _msttexthash=\"13213317\" _msthash=\"103\" style=\"margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">Choosing <a href=\"https://www.decathlon.vn/vi/shop/decathlon-hiking-trekking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"\">hiking gear</a> needs to have a balance between fashion and product quality, helping to protect the body while ensuring the most comfortable exercise.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-block-start: var(--wp--preset--spacing--small); margin-block-end: 0px; max-width: var(--wp--style--global--content-size); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" oxygen-sans,=\"\" ubuntu,=\"\" cantarell,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;=\"\" margin-left:=\"\