(16, 'Indonesian Mountain Guide Association (IMGA)', 'Dra. Zannuba Arifah CH. R.', 'The Indonesian Mountain Guide Association, known locally as Asosiasi Pemandu Gunung Indonesia (APGI), certifies mountain guides in Indonesia. This certification is vital for guides working in the region, ensuring they have the necessary skills and knowledge for guiding clients safely in mountainous terrain. The guides affiliated with APGI have extensive experience in leading expeditions both domestically and internationally, emphasizing their expertise and passion for mountain guiding', '<p>Office IVBV/UIAGM/IFMGA\r\nChristoph Schaub\r\nRue du Léman 30\r\nCH-1920 Martigny\r\nSwitzerland\r\n</p><p>\r\n+41 79 279 66 24\r\n</p><p>Email: office@uiagm.info</p><p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;https://www.facebook.com/IndonesianMountainGuideAssociation/&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:1057409,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;16&quot;:14,&quot;23&quot;:1}\" data-sheets-hyperlink=\"https://www.facebook.com/IndonesianMountainGuideAssociation/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; color: rgb(5, 99, 193);\"><a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/IndonesianMountainGuideAssociation/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/IndonesianMountainGuideAssociation/</a></span><br></p><p>\r\n                                        </p>', '1709629899_24.png', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2766.24436555584!2d7.069567987233829!3d46.10603749655391!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x478ec9c323c6c3bd%3A0x8185645e6ca584da!2sRue%20du%20L%C3%A9man%2030%2C%201920%20Martigny%2C%20Switzerland!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1709203501258!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-d