(26, 'Himalayan Experience (Himex)', 'Russell Brice', '<span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Himalayan Experience, commonly referred to as Himex, is a company that specializes in organizing and leading expeditions in the Himalayas, including to some of the world\'s highest and most challenging mountains like Mount Everest. Founded by Russell Brice, a renowned mountaineer with extensive experience in Himalayan climbing, Himex is known for its commitment to safety, environmental responsibility, and providing clients with a high level of support and expertise.\\r\\n\\r\\nHimex offers a range of services to climbers and adventurers, from logistical support and guiding to full expedition management. The company caters to climbers of various skill levels, from novices seeking their first Himalayan experience to seasoned mountaineers attempting to summit Everest. Himex\'s expeditions are carefully planned and executed, with attention to detail in aspects such as acclimatization schedules, weather forecasting, and route selection to maximize safety and success rates.\\r\\n\\r\\nOne of the distinguishing features of Himalayan Experience is its emphasis on using experienced guides and high-quality equipment. The company also strives to minimize its environmental impact on the fragile Himalayan ecosystem through sustainable practices and supports local communities by hiring local staff and contributing to local economies.\\r\\n\\r\\nHimalayan Experience has been featured in various documentaries and news articles for its expeditions and for the role it plays in promoting responsible and sustainable mountaineering in the Himalayas. Despite the inherent risks of high-altitude climbing, Himex\'s approach to expedition planning and execution has earned it a reputation for reliability and professionalism in the mountaineering community.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:9089,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;16&quot;:14}\" style=\"\">Himalayan Experience, commonly referred to as Himex, is a company that specializes in organizing and leading expeditions in the Himalayas, including to some of the world\'s highest and most challenging mountains like Mount Everest. Founded by Russell Brice, a renowned mountaineer with extensive experience in Himalayan climbing, Himex is known for its commitment to safety, environmental responsibility, and providing clients with a high level of support and expertise.<br><br>Himex offers a range of services to climbers and adventurers, from logistical support and guiding to full expedition management. The company caters to climbers of various skill levels, from novices seeking their first Himalayan experience to seasoned mountaineers attempting to summit Everest. Himex\'s expeditions are carefully planned and executed, with attention to detail in aspects such as acclimatization schedules, weather forecasting, and route selection to maximize safety and success rates.<br><br>One of the distinguishing features of Himalayan Experience is its emphasis on using experienced guides and high-quality equipment. The company also strives to minimize its environmental impact on the fragile Himalayan ecosystem through sustainable practices and supports local communities by hiring local staff and contributing to local economies.<br><br>Himalayan Experience has been featured in various documentaries and news articles for its expeditions and for the role it plays in promoting responsible and sustainable mountaineering in the Himalayas. Despite the inherent risks of high-altitude climbing, Himex\'s approach to expedition planning and execution has earned it a reputation for reliability and professionalism in the mountaineering community.</span>', '<span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Scheulingstrasse 390, Mayrhofen, Austria\\r\\n\\r\\n+43 664 1200735\\r\\n\\r\\ninfo@hi