(27, 'Madison Mountaineering', 'Garrett Madison', '<span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Madison Mountaineering is a renowned mountain guide service and expedition company known for leading high-altitude climbing expeditions around the world. Founded by Garrett Madison, one of America\'s premier expedition leaders and a highly respected figure in the international mountaineering community, the company specializes in guiding clients to the summit of some of the world\'s most challenging and iconic peaks. Garrett Madison has a notable record of leading successful expeditions to Mount Everest and other 8000-meter peaks, and he and his team are recognized for their expertise, safety standards, and commitment to clients. Madison Mountaineering offers expeditions to Everest, K2, Lhotse, and other significant mountains, providing comprehensive support that includes pre-expedition training, logistics management, and a focus on safety and client success. Their services appeal to both experienced climbers seeking to tackle the world\'s highest peaks and adventurers looking to embark on their first high-altitude climbs under the guidance of experienced professionals.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:9089,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;16&quot;:14}\" style=\"\">Madison Mountaineering is a renowned mountain guide service and expedition company known for leading high-altitude climbing expeditions around the world. Founded by Garrett Madison, one of America\'s premier expedition leaders and a highly respected figure in the international mountaineering community, the company specializes in guiding clients to the summit of some of the world\'s most challenging and iconic peaks. Garrett Madison has a notable record of leading successful expeditions to Mount Everest and other 8000-meter peaks, and he and his team are recognized for their expertise, safety standards, and commitment to clients. Madison Mountaineering offers expeditions to Everest, K2, Lhotse, and other significant mountains, providing comprehensive support that includes pre-expedition training, logistics management, and a focus on safety and client success. Their services appeal to both experienced climbers seeking to tackle the world\'s highest peaks and adventurers looking to embark on their first high-altitude climbs under the guidance of experienced professionals.</span>', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;\\nP.O. Box 1045\\nJackson, WY  83001\\n+1 206-494-5799\\ninfo@madisonmountaineering.com&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:8833,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;16&quot;:14}\" style=\"\">P.O. Box 1045<br>Jackson, WY 83001<br>+1 206-494-5799<br>info@madisonmountaineering.com</span></p><p><a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"https://madisonmountaineering.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; background-color: rgb(63, 71, 78);\">https://madisonmountaineering.com/</a></p><p>\r\n                                        </p>', '1709632536_35.png', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2686.0358369237956!2d-122.35815208880928!3d47.68372398252948!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x54901424b6a503d1%3A0x593bebf1a34f71a7!2sMadison%20Mountaineering!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1709632494441!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', 0, NULL),
(28, 'Damavand Mountain Climbing and Skiing Club', 'Hayleh Manteghi', '<span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;The Damavand Mountaineering and Ski Club (DMSC) is an organization that likely focuses on outdoor activities related to mountaineering and skiing, with a specific emphasis on Mount Damavand. Mount Damavand, standing at 5,610 meters (18,406 ft), is the highest peak in Iran and the Middle East, and the highest volcano in Asia. It\'s a significant landmark and a popular destination for trekking, mountaineering, and skiing enthusiasts.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhile I don\'t have real-time or specific data about the DMSC, such clubs typically offer a range of services and activities, including:\\r\\n\\r\\n- Organized climbs and ski trips to Mount Damavand and possibly other locations.\\r\\n- Training and educational programs related to mountaineering, skiing, and outdoor survival skills.\\r\\n- Environmental conservation efforts aimed at preserving the natural beauty and ecological health of Mount Damavand and surrounding areas.\\r\\n- Community events, meetings, and social gatherings for members to share experiences, learn from each other, and plan future activities.\\r\\n\\r\\nMembership in such clubs often provides access to experienced guides, safety training, and a community of like-minded individuals passionate about the outdoors and mountain sports. The DMSC would likely aim to promote safe and responsible mountaineering and skiing practices, while also encouraging the exploration and enjoyment of Iran\'s highest peak and its surrounding natural landscape.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:9089,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;16&quot;:14}\" style=\"\">The Damavand Mountaineering and Ski Club (DMSC) is an organization that likely focuses on outdoor activities related to mountaineering and skiing, with a specific emphasis on Mount Damavand. Mount Damavand, standing at 5,610 meters (18,406 ft), is the highest peak in Iran and the Middle East, and the highest volcano in Asia. It\'s a significant landmark and a popular destination for trekking, mountaineering, and skiing enthusiasts.<br><br>While I don\'t have real-time or specific data about the DMSC, such clubs typically offer a range of services and activities, including:<br><br>Organized climbs and ski trips to Mount Damavand and possibly other locations.<br>Training and educational programs related to mountaineering, skiing, and outdoor survival skills.<br>Environmental conservation efforts aimed at preserving the natural beauty and ecological health of Mount Damavand and surrounding areas.<br>Community events, meetings, and social gatherings for members to share experiences, learn from each other, and plan future activities.<br><br>Membership in such clubs often provides access to experienced guides, safety training, and a community of like-minded individuals passionate about the outdoors and mountain sports. The DMSC would likely aim to promote safe and responsible mountaineering and skiing practices, while also encouraging the exploration and enjoyment of Iran\'s highest peak and its surrounding natural landscape.</span>', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;info@damavandclub.ir\\n66717639 fax: 66743444\\n3rd Floor, No. 679, First Lalehzarno, Enghelab St., Tehran, Iran&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:9089,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;16&quot;:14}\" style=\"\">info@damavandclub.ir<br>66717639 fax: 66743444<br>3rd Floor, No. 679, First Lalehzarno, Enghelab St., Tehran, Iran</span></p><p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;info@damavandclub.ir\\n66717639 fax: 66743444\\n3rd Floor, No. 679, First Lalehzarno, Enghelab St., Tehran, Iran&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:908